description: Welcome to 58 Telegraph Street, Unit 2! This spacious one bedroom, one bathroom condo is nestled in the heart of South Boston. The newly renovated bathroom offers a soothing spa like atmosphere, ready to help you relax after your most challenging day. Enjoy your morning coffee on the recently updated, oversized composite deck. Come inside and discover a bright, open concept living area with soaring ceilings and recessed lighting, perfect for entertaining or unwinding. The well-appointed kitchen showcases sleek countertops, upgraded cabinets, and modern appliances making dinner prep a breeze. Less than a block from Thomas Park and just minutes to the beach— this location is ideal and offers easy access to all the best restaurants, bars and entertainment that Southie has to offer. This is the urban lifestyle opportunity you have been waiting for, do not miss this home!
